Implemented learning features
Auth: register, login, logout, verify email, forgot/reset password, bcrypt, rate limits
RBAC: USER / SELLER / ADMIN (admin only via seed — no public signup)
Listings: CRUD service, search/filters, featured/trending, view counts
AI: listing assistant, NL search, chat, moderation + embeddings (worker)
Workers: email outbox (Mailpit), background jobs table
Frontend: homepage, search, listing detail, categories, auth, sell, favorites, admin scaffold
